              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Using Ru carrier and 106Ru tracer. One part of",
                " the solution was analyzed for Ru, another part was",
                " assayed for monitors 97Zr and 104Tc."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Fission rate determination: by 97Zr and 104Tc monitors;",
